<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，其他弟子都睡着了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空却一直醒着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凌晨三点钟的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地穿过一片漆黑的庙宇，走进了菩提祖师的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，你来这里干什么？”菩提祖师问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明白了您给我的暗示。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在我的脑袋上敲了三下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这就是说您让我在凌晨三点钟的时候来找您。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在您可以教我长生不老之术了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师微笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是个值得一教的弟子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过来，离我近一点。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师对着悟空耳语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师轻声念了经文，也念了关于宇宙自然的秘诀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空听着师父的话，强光照着整个房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，悟空知道怎样才能长生不老了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在后来的几年里，悟空一直在冥想并练习秘诀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他弟子晚上睡觉的时候，悟空却一直醒着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他的身体都充满了力量，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想变成什么就能变成什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可以变成其他动物，在空中飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，所有的弟子都坐在外边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，”有个弟子说，“你最近很忙啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是呀，”另一个弟子说，“你在忙些什么啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在冥想和练习秘诀。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“秘诀？”第一个弟子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人看上去都非常感兴趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们坐得离悟空更近了些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，”悟空说，“师父告诉了我秘诀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他告诉你了？”一个弟子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定是个特别的弟子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不是每个人都可以从他那里学到秘诀的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他教了你什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空微笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“长生不老的方法。他还教了我怎么变法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我们看看你的本事吧！”那个弟子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空站起身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低声念了个短咒，又做了个手势。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，嘶的一声！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他原来的位置上立着一棵巨大的松树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>松树发出了悟空的声音：“怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弟子们拍手欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太神奇了！”有个弟子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空真的很厉害！”另一个弟子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的叫声让师父听到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师走出屋子，看到了那棵巨大的松树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么回事？”他大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都停止了欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空迅速变回了自己原来的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师的眼里冒着怒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了悟空，所有人给我进屋去！”他高声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师等着其他所有弟子离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我教给你秘密的口诀是让你可以长生不老。”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是让你来炫耀的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”悟空说，“我......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师继续说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在所有弟子都见过你的本事了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也会想要学！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你不告诉他们，他们可能会伤害你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不能再留在这里了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这儿你会遇到危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须离开。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空开始哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，师父！我要去哪里呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回家吧！”菩提祖师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您教了我这么多！”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须先报答您。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不需要报答我。”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要别惹麻烦就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师盯着悟空看了一会儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后说道：“我已经看到，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，你会做坏事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要告诉任何人你是我的弟子。走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空低下了头：“再见，师父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳上一朵云，离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没过多久，悟空就到了花果山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我回来了！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长臂猿跑向了他：“大王！不好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>